591
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:31,390
Hindi ko na siya mahahanap.

592
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:33,950
Xu, anong sinasabi mo?

593
00:42:39,310 --> 00:42:40,390
Xu, ikaw...

594
00:42:47,310 --> 00:42:48,150
Xu.

595
00:42:49,350 --> 00:42:50,190
Xu.

596
00:42:50,660 --> 00:42:51,500
Xu, anong meron?

597
00:42:52,350 --> 00:42:53,350
Xu, gising na.

598
00:42:53,750 --> 00:42:54,590
Xu.

599
00:42:54,950 --> 00:42:55,790
Xu.

600
00:42:58,720 --> 00:43:04,050
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

601
00:43:04,380 --> 00:43:08,630
♪Light encountered shadow♪

602
00:43:09,990 --> 00:43:15,360
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

603
00:43:15,660 --> 00:43:20,260
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

604
00:43:21,350 --> 00:43:23,190
♪Biglang basag♪

605
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:40,840
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

606
00:43:41,020 --> 00:43:45,350
♪Light encountered shadow♪

607
00:43:46,720 --> 00:43:52,110
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

608
00:43:52,340 --> 00:43:56,280
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

609
00:43:58,050 --> 00:43:59,940
♪Biglang basag♪

610
00:44:02,600 --> 00:44:05,760
♪Makinig, umaatungal ang lahat ng tunog♪

611
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:08,290
♪Habang ang malamig na yelo ay nagiging tides♪

612
00:44:08,290 --> 00:44:13,810
♪Ang kalungkutan ng isang siglo ay nakakatunaw ng mga pangarap♪

613
00:44:13,810 --> 00:44:17,050
♪Pagsunod sa patnubay ng tadhana♪

614
00:44:17,050 --> 00:44:21,910
♪Sa tadhana, ang ating mga sandali ay ipinagpalit♪

615
00:44:22,250 --> 00:44:25,270
♪Nagising ang puso bigla♪

616
00:44:25,270 --> 00:44:28,090
♪Panoorin ang pagbagsak ng mga paputok na parang bituin♪

617
00:44:28,350 --> 00:44:30,880
♪Ang bono na ito ay gusot sa isang thread♪

618
00:44:30,880 --> 00:44:36,300
♪Ang mga makamundong pagmuni-muni ay kumukupas sa ambon♪

619
00:44:36,470 --> 00:44:39,540
♪Pahiram ng isang panandaliang tibok ng puso♪

620
00:44:39,700 --> 00:44:44,600
♪Dinala mo ako sa mortal na alikabok,
hanggang sa nabighani ako sa mga alindog nito♪

621
